Package: movMFnoise
Type: Package
Title: Mixtures of von Mises-Fisher Distributions with a Noise Component
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrea", "Cappozzo", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "andrea.cappozzo@polimi.it"))
Description: Provides functions for fitting mixtures of von Mises-Fisher 
    distributions with a noise component (uniform density on the sphere). 
    The package implements an EM algorithm for parameter estimation and 
    includes functions for data simulation and visualization.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
